title: Ashley Graham shares nude snap on Valentine's Day
text:
Ashley Graham delighted her fans by sharing a nude snap of herself on Valentine's Day.
Surrounded by colorful hearts the plus-size model had added to the image she shared via Instagram Stories , the 28-year-old is seen posing with her hands covering her breasts and her left leg positioned to protect her modesty.
The snap was taken during her shoot for designer Prabal Gurung for their new Lane Bryant Collection that debuted during New York Fashion Week on Sunday.
Instagram Stories gift: Ashley Graham delighted her fans by sharing a nude snap of herself on Valentine's Day. It was taken during her Prabal Gurung Lane Bryant Collection shoot last month
The brunette beauty is all smiles as she looks directly into the camera while completely naked. Gurung is positioned behind her with his back to thelens.
Ashley's hair is loose and falling down her back and her lips are wet with gloss.
Last month, the body confident model had shared a close-up snap of herself on vacation that showed cellulite on her thighs.
She wrote next to the snap: 'I workout. I do my best to eat well. I love the skin I'm in. And I'm not ashamed of a few lumps, bumps or cellulite... and you shouldn't be either.'
Plus-size model: Ashley, 28, wowed in a black dress and animal-print duster as she supported the collection's debut during New York Fashion Week on Sunday
High profile: On Tuesday, the brunette beauty flashed her midriff in a cropped turtleneck sweater and black jeans with a varsity jacket as she attended the Coach show during NYFW
Ashley has been enjoying viewing the runway shows duringg New York Fashion Week.
She looked elegant in a black dress with patterned duster at Gurung's show on Sunday.
And on Tuesday, she attended the Coach show in a cropped brown turtleneck sweater paired with black jeans and a black, brown and white varsity jacket.
'Dream come true': Ashley posed with several other celebrity models for the cover of Vogue
